#-Function--cln
  Function: cln
      Desc: Remove all *~ files recursively from current directory.
          : CLNTEMPFILES array defines temporary files, default is ( '*~' '~*' '.~*' )
          : Recursively remove all temporary files ( ${CLNTEMPFILES[@]} )"
          : Defaults: maxdepth 2, verbose enabled, dryrun enabled'
          : More than one dirspec can be specified. Default is current directory.'
          : if defined, CLNTEMPFILES envar sets temporary files to search for. Default is ( '*~' '~*' '.~*' )"
#-Function--cln---------------------------------------------------------------
